                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4027" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0988</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9782 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小米之家如何引领小米的商业模式创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How the Mi Home Led the Business Model Innovation in MI Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">马向阳，朱耀荣，于波</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京小米科技有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">22 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小米之家；新零售；小米；商业模式创新；二手资料撰写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Mi Home; New retailing; MI Group; Business model innovation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015至2016年，“风口”渐变，小米陷入出货量与市场份额下滑的困境。在内外部因素的驱动下，小米最终走上了变革之路；由小米之家所引爆的新零售格局，成为小米这轮变革的桥头堡。“牵一发而动全身”：新零售的推进，促成了并有赖于小米各个方面的改变与努力；而小米之家的建设，也与其他维度的创新举措完成了对接与会合。新零售实现了小米商业利益的再次采掘与巨大释放，在其引领下，小米的商业模式完成了整体性的创新。本案例从小米进行商业模式创新的动因出发，展现了小米之家如何运营与打造、小米新零售如何落地与发展，并探讨了小米之家的建设如何撬动起小米整体的商业模式创新，也即商业模式创新的路径。本案例是企业通过开展商业模式创新破局新零售的典型案例，可以帮助学生更深入地了解新零售，更深刻地理解新零售引致商业模式创新的逻辑。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">From 2015 to 2016, under the qualitative change of marketing environment, MI fell into the plight of declining shipments and market share. Driven by internal and external factors, MI eventually embarked on the road of reform its business model, and the &quot;new retailing&quot; strategy triggered by Mi Home grew into the bridgehead of this round of change. &quot;A slight move in one part may affect the situation as a whole&quot;: the implementation of &quot;new retailing&quot; strategy has contributed to and depended on the changes and efforts of overall commercial aspects of MI, and the project of Mi Home has also achieved the docking and convergence with other dimensions of innovative initiatives. &quot;New retailing&quot; practice has realized the re-exploitation and huge release of MI’s commercial interests. Under this guidance, MI’s business model has completed the overall innovation. Starting from the motivation of MI’s business model innovation, this case shows how Mi Home is operated, how MI’s &quot;new retailing&quot; practice is developed. This case also explores how the project of Mi Home can lead MI’s business model innovation as a whole, that is, the path of business model innovation. This case is typical for situations that enterprises carry out &quot;new retailing&quot; practice and business model innovation, which can help students acquainted with &quot;new retailing&quot; more deeply and taken in the logic that how &quot;new retailing&quot; practice leads to the business model innovation more profoundly.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新管理》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
